{"tid":1468344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好打記者同救護員","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:51:42.000Z","uid":264051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9df91cca7ebc2c68424f173061f8f0a3c446f1ba","tid":1468344,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:56.000Z","msg":"我係P牌，預左俾人屌<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想割席<br />\n但我希望各位唔好因為衝動或者有不滿而走去攻擊記者同救護員<br />\n<br />\n如果有人咁做，麻煩拉一拉開佢，就當係保護手足唔受傷害，佢都係繼續嘗試去攻擊的話，咁佢就一定唔係同路人，只係黎搞事<br />\n<br />\n（假記者另計，麻煩打多兩野）"},{"pid":"b9d9edf2d3c6eb387cf858a2738622120fd26fbb","tid":1468344,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:27:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d42e5560f36384f47622412df8b3a53f20f146e4","tid":1468344,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:28:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28cf1b1fbde53d71ef8c1882105d4687a10fb12b","tid":1468344,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:31:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97125e8baf5d9993d1a4266dc2af2b2804b4e110","tid":1468344,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:34:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd1994291db8aca4b5dfc2d2dfb0fead3e76701e","tid":1468344,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:36:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c2e230ac31fe1874547b3a20bbb6ac83506b7cc","tid":1468344,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e8af3c86835a2e8a531663cfeda7b2154b4fc69","tid":1468344,"uid":264051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:51:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}